    slug: "botox-personal-brand-men",
    title: "Botox and Personal Branding: How Appearance Shapes Your Professional Identity",
    metaTitle: "Botox for Men's Personal Brand — Appearance, Confidence & Career",
    description: "In the age of LinkedIn headshots, video calls, and personal branding, how you look directly affects how you're perceived professionally. Here's the honest case for why men's aesthetics and personal brand are inextricably connected.",
